---
layout: page
meta_title: Donor wall
meta_description: All our wonderful donors
title: Donor wall
---

{% set money_raised = data.summary.donations.donorbox.amount + data.summary.donations.sponsors.amount %}
{% set num_donors = data.summary.donations.donorbox.donors + data.summary.donations.sponsors.donors %}

<main id="main" class="main flex flex-1 h-full flex-col focus:outline-none" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto justify-center text-center px-4 pt-6 md:pt-16">
        <div class="md:w-4/5 lg:w-2/3 mx-auto justify-center text-center">
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold pb-2 lg:pb-6">{{ num_donors | thousands }} wonderful donors have raised £{{ money_raised | thousands }} so far.</h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 pb-4">The level of public generosity has blown away. So many beautiful comments and generous gifts make all the difference to the heroes we're feeding.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% include "components/donation_button.njk" %}
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto px-4 flex justify-center text-center pt-6 md:pt-12 lg:pb-8 flex flex-col">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold pb-2">{{ data.donors.records | length }} of our donors' messages to our NHS heroes</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 pb-4">We'll update messages periodically. Your message won't show up immediately, please bear with us!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto px-4 pb-6 md:pb-16">
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center">
            {% for campaign in data.donors.records %}
                <li class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 flex p-2 md:p-3">
                    <div class="border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-2xl rounded-lg flex-grow bg-white flex flex-col">
                        <div class="p-4 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                            <h4 class="text-gray-600 text-base pb-2">{{ campaign.fields["First Name"] }} gave £{{ campaign.fields["Amount"] | thousands }}</h4>
                            {% if campaign.fields["Donor Comment"] %}
                                <p class="lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl">{{ campaign.fields["Donor Comment"] | truncate(300) }}</p>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </div>
</main>